  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An attack on Gota Gogama, Matara",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The organizers say that some group attacked Matara Gotagogama last night.",
        "A group of about six people who arrived in a luxury jeep showed a knife and scared a young man away and caused damage to the premises.",
        "Banners and cutouts drawn and exhibited by the struggling youth were also cut and damaged.",
        "It is not yet known who did this.",
        "However, the attack took place at a time when the organizers had decided to evacuate the Matara Gotagogama premises yesterday (24).",
        "On the 16th of last April, Mr. Sarath Vemalasuriya, a retired medical officer, started Matara Gotagogama near the Matara main bus stand and yesterday (24) was supposed to complete 100 days."
      ],
